#: ../../source/install/install-common-intro.rst:1
msgid ""
"A complete Mattermost installation consists of three major components: a "
"proxy server, a database server, and the Mattermost server. You can "
"install all components on one machine, or you can install each component "
"on its own machine. If you have only two machines, then install the proxy"
" and the Mattermost server on one machine, and install the database on "
"the other machine."
